{td}Operator can assess all critical conditions at a glance without navigating multiple screens{/td}
{td}Consolidated single-page layout is critical for non-technical users. Must show sensor readings, alerts, and actuator status. Validated by stakeholder survey - operators need to assess all parameters in one view. 'Simple' should be defined in acceptance criteria (e.g., max 2 taps to reach any key metric).{/td}
{td}{status:PROPOSED|color=Yellow}{/td}
