{td}Requirement analyzed and refined. Decomposed into: User = business owner/operator, Action = export raw sensor data to Excel/CSV, Circumstances = compliance record-keeping or regulatory/advisory meeting preparation, Outcome = structured data available for external sharing with authorities and professionals. ATTENTION: GMS-44 (SHR-49) was marked INVALID as a duplicate absorbed into GMS-43. This ticket covers overlapping scope. Team must confirm at review: does unique scope remain (compliance-specific regulatory output) vs GMS-43's updated coverage? If not, this ticket should be marked INVALID. Minimum fields: timestamp, sensor ID, parameter name, value, unit per R5. Moving to Proposed pending team scope review.{/td}
